_:Nbdacaac8683849ba810d5b935f5eb14b <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Samantha Dixon was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State in the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government on 6 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>She was previously Vice-Chamberlain of HM Household (Government Whip) between 10 July 2024 and 6 September 2025. She was elected as the MP for Chester North and Neston in July 2024.</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
